Why did I chose marketing for a degree? I mean I love it, but it is the 4th year I have done it now.

Well I better get back to revising!

I've also set up a diaryland account because they are way more easier to use. Will still undate this one: crashedstar.diaryland.com.

Chuss! xx [GEEK]

Shit, I am SOOOOOOOOO stupid. Total total blondey day. [Please note, I am not actually blonde... I was just born blonde]

Well today was work [sigh]. It was a bit of a boring day, but I dunno... work just seems more fun now. I went out to get Rhys a bag for school he had made me get from Topman, walked back up on my way to Accessories busy talking on my phone, slid and nearly fell on my ARSE! How embarrasing!

Not only that, I managed to leave change behind the back at the end of the day. I feel so stooooopid!

Anyway, besides that, it's been a good day! I'm in a good mood, for once and I am actually enjoying work... wooo!

Now I have a comm studies deadline tomorrow to look forward to AND an english deadline AND a important exam on WEDNESDAY. Oh joy!

xx

Mum still violently ignoring me, refusing my existance. Fuck her. 

Have lots of homework to keep me busy. English and Communication Studies deadline for Mon, BS Thematic Enquiry exam on Wednesday. I am SO going to fail.

Well I am knackered! Going back to bed now, won't be able to sleep but oh well.
